publicVariable 
Behavior: global 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.34) 
Description: Broadcast variable value to all computers. 
Only type Number is supported in version 1.33 and before. 
Following Types are supported since version 1.34:  Number Boolean 
 Object Group 
Following Types are supported since version ArmA v1.00:  String 
Since version ArmA v1.09:Any value can be transferred, including 
 Array  Code 
The only limitation is you cannot transfer references to entities 
 which are local, like scripts, displays, or local objects. 
 
 
Syntax:  
 publicVariable varName 
Parameters: 
varName: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing